<p>Test passes if the following texts are identical:</p>

<div class="test"><body>
  </body><p><span class="tcy">170141183460469231731687303715884105727</span></p>
  <p>2014</p>
</div>

</body><body>

<p>Test passes if the following texts are identical:</p>

<div class="test">
  <p><span class="tcy">2014</span></p>
  <p>2014</p>
</div>

</body><body>

<p>Test passes if the following texts are identical:</p>

<div class="test">
  <p><span class="tcy">2014</span></p>
  <p>2014</p>
</div>

</body><body>

<style>
.test {
  writing-mode: horizontal-tb;
  font-size: 9223372036854775808em;
  line-height: 129;
  direction: rtl;
}

.tcy {
  text-combine-upright: all;
}
</style>

<div class="test">
  <p><span class="tcy">2014</span></p>
  <p><p><p><p>2014</p></p></p></p>
</div>

